{"name":"Dirty Fighter","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Those with this Edge will do anything to win a fight. The dastardly cur is particularly good at tricks. He adds +2 to rolls when performing a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.z8VbTEJUItMTSxNw]{Test} with the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.MIvf1ckXhEyM27uv]{Fighting} skill.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172248,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"6edBOOcUGBgBYHiA","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Frenzy","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.DugtMFQnsmkUnQiv"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A character with Frenzy rolls a second @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} die with any one of his Fighting attacks for the turn. The extra die may be allocated to the same or different targets as he sees fit. Resolve each separately</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172283,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"6qE3qBxU9AezMHJC","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
