{"_id":"7rQPzczYHPfjymQL","name":"Rabble-Rouser","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-unity-alliance.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tbo7kidroy","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Social Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.WJdZ5HttGFp7lpEp"},"journal-links":{}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This instigator knows how to rile up several enemies at once.</p>\n<p>Once per turn, a character with this Edge can make a social @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Test]{Test} with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Intimidation]{Intimidation}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Persuasion]{Persuasion}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Performance]{Performance} against all enemies in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Medium Blast Template}. The targets must be able to see and hear the hero clearly. Each defender resists and is affected by the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Test]{Test} separately.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Social Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173179,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Lunge","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A lunge allows a swordsman to extend the reach of his weapon. The character gains +1 @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Reach]{Reach} to his weapon. He may not use this Edge with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.First Strike]{First Strike}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Frenzy]{Frenzy}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Sweep]{Sweep}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Fighting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Lankhmar"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172404,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"7y5S0hjmKXgXhqie","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Cry Havoc!","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The general has an uncanny knack for knowing when to unleash his troops and when to hold back.</p>\n<p>Once per battle, during the Battle Roll Phase, the character may declare a charge. He must do this before he or his opponent rolls their Battle die. If the character succeeds in his roll and beats his opponent, his enemy loses one extra token.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Spirit d8+, Fervor, Battle d10+"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172746,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"8djeGUZAe2QuEQrV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Running Throw","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nsyr9ljpuke","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Species Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The hero knows how to use his momentum to boost the range of thrown weapons.</p>\n<p>If the character moves at least half his @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#movement]{Pace} immediately before making a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} roll to throw a weapon he increases the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Range]{Range} of his thrown weapon by 2/4/8. No other actions may be performed between moving and throwing, and the two maneuvers must be taken in the same round.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Bugbear, Half-orc, or Orc, Strength d8, Athletics d8"},"grants":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173265,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"8gtMsfOgeSCPGM2D","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Holy/Unholy Warrior","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-silhouette.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ce260dx4lpo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.s0Njz8jYl74dWnSW"},"journal-links":{}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Believers face grave dangers in service to their divine patrons. To survive such hardships, the forces of good (or evil) grant miracles and the ability to turn their favor into supernatural protection. </span></p>\n<p>The chosen may add +1 to the total of a final @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#soak-rolls]{Soak roll} for each Power Point spent, to a maximum of +4.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Power Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Any) or Mystic Powers (Any), Vow (to your Deity)"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172919,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"8wcfJ6D3zB5ANOuw","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
