{"name":"Improved Dodge","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.jwhtH1wbKoDSN4w1"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The hero adds +2 when Evading area effect attacks. See </span><strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Evasion]{Evasion}</span></strong>.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Dodge"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172317,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"95A45Dz5kzISVeC6","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Blind Fighting","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Blind fighters have trained long and hard to fight with out being able to see, using smell, sound, disturbances in the surrounding air, etc. You character is able to halves any penalties for @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Illumination]{Illumination}.</p>\n<p>Note this edge does not allow you to see in the dark only to fight at a reduced penalty when you vision is impaired.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Agility d8+, Notice d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Legends of Steel"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172188,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"95KbGA5T5Bnze0da","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Natural Leader","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.PJgKPcidJlHxZoHf"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This leader has proven herself time and time again, gaining the respect of all those who fight by her side.</span></p>\n<p>Any Leadership Edge that says it applies only to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Wild Cards and Extras]{Extras} now applies to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Wild Cards and Extras]{Wild Cards} as well.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Spirit d8+, Command"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172785,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"9QhHh9Lkg4L9FaRk","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Brawler","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"kjzlcYkuLXL4NwhC","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.toughness.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Brawler","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.q5NKwGPeK9PKQdIb"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>His fists hit like hammers or his talons cut like scythes. His body feels like it's made of stone. Brawlers increase their @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1 Making Characters]{Toughness} by 1 and roll @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Strength} +d4 when hitting with their fists or feet (or claws if they have them). If they already have a damage die from <strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Natural Weapons]{Claws}</strong>, the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Martial Artist]{Martial Artist} Edge, etc., increase the damage die type by one instead.</p>\n<p>The Brawler Edge doesn't make the character's fists <strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Natural Weapons]{Natural Weapons}</strong></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Strength d8+, Vigor d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172200,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"9brebtx25RTPsYrJ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mark of Handling","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the following powers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Beast Friend]{beast friend}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Boost/Lower Trait]{boost Trait}</em> (<em>@UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Agility}, @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Strength}<em>, @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Vigor}</em>, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.SzVzIV8ZxqKg3Oe3]{Athletics}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.MIvf1ckXhEyM27uv]{Fighting}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice},</em> and <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}</em> on animals only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Empathy]{empathy}</em> (animals only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Summon Animal]{summon animal}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Boost/Lower Trait]{Boost Trait}</em> has the range of touch only, but the heir gains no benefit from the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Limitations]{Limitation}.</p>\n<p>The heir has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. She automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Raises]{raise} for 2 additional Power Points. She may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>The @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Vadalis]{Mark of Handling} doesn't grant access to Edges requiring an Arcane Background. If the heir also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges, abilities, or Power Points can be used with the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Vadalis]{Mark of Handling} (and vice-versa).</p>\n<p>Additionally, pick any one of the following skills: @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Animal Handling]{Animal Handling}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Riding]{Riding}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}, and add +1 to the total whenever they are used.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Human"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172618,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"9v4hFaBHQDzziyZm","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Greater Mark of Detection","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the additional following power:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Divination]{divination}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>She may now also access any Epic Power modifiers to any powers offered by his dragonmark.</p>\n<p>Additionally the dragonmarked heir gains 5 more Power Points for her dragonmarked powers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mark of Detection"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172552,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"9wF5RShwXOMcS82S","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Weapon Master","type":"edge","img":"icons/sundries/flags/banner-symbol-axe-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_fsvlz5d67ma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Legendary Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.QOfkvoRItZh3Hjey"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The warrior increases his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Characters]{Parry} by +1 and the bonus damage die for @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} rolls is a d8 instead of a d6 (see <strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Dealing Damage]{Bonus Damage}</strong>). He must be armed to gain these benefits, but this includes the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Martial Artist]{Martial Artist} Edge, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Special Ability (Claws)]{claws}, or other abilities that count as weapons.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Legendary Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Legendary, Fighting d12+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172856,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"A6Lrm5keeGFnd9Q1","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
