{"name":"Elemental Master","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/elements-air-earth-fire-water.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Elementalists must choose an elemental origin when they become mages: earth, fire, water, or air. This Edge grants them domain over another elemental force. They may change the Trappings of their powers between the elements they&rsquo;ve mastered at will.</p>\n<p>Elemental Master may be taken multiple times to gain all four elements (or more if such exist in the Dungeon Master&rsquo;s world).</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Elementalist)"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171804,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"B6b3mDXyucuU52NT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
