{"name":"Adamantine Body","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","effects":[{"_id":"N93Ig1bYA5YgBt7D","flags":{},"changes":[{"key":"system.stats.toughness.armor","mode":2,"value":"4","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","label":"Adamantine Body","tint":null,"transfer":true,"origin":null}],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nsyr9ljpuke","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Species Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The warforged was created from a specially designed line made with adamantine giving him +4 @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Armor]{Armor} instead of the normal +2 from Composite Plating.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> This Edge must be taken during character creation.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Savage Eberron</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Species Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Warforged"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173233,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"QcyEinYFMpf7uquT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Greater Mark of Finding","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the additional following power:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Farsight]{farsight}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Farsight]{Farsight}</em> has the range of touch only, but the heir gains no benefit from the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Limitations]{Limitation}.</p>\n<p>He may now also access any Epic Power modifiers to any powers offered by his dragonmark.</p>\n<p>Additionally the dragonmarked heir gains 5 more Power Points for his dragonmarked powers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mark of Finding"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172555,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"QnN1tkX1T5KtrK5G","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Improved Counterattack","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.D31binNUzouqkOMQ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The hero gets a </span><strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Free Attacks]{Free Attack} </strong></span>against up to three failed attacks each round.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Counterattack"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172314,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"QoqSfHytWsCYQgYL","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Chemist","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/toxins/cauldron-pot-bubbles-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The alchemist&rsquo;s concoctions last one week rather than 48 hours when given to others.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Arcane Background (Alchemist), Alchemy d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171766,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"Qpxgl7QRc4eB5nTW","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Trademark Weapon","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"viA65GSpKV0IFwsX","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Trademark Readied Weapon","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.QHBtO0jmIzfl8TDE"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The hero knows one unique weapon (Excalibur, Old Betsy, Sting) like the back of his hand. When using it, he adds +1 to his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} (throwing), @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Shooting]{Shooting} rolls, and +1 to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Characters]{Parry} when readied (even if it's a ranged weapon).</span></p>\n<p>A fighter can take this Edge multiple times, applying it to a different weapon each time. If a Trademark Weapon is lost, he can replace it but the benefits don't kick in for a few days (however long the DM feels is dramatically appropriate).</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, skill with chosen weapon of d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172520,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"R40eEXUBkuDJR2ol","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"War Cry","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nsyr9ljpuke","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Species Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Bugbear, Half-orc, and Orc can bellow an ear-splitting, nervewracking war cry that has been known to send lesser foes fleeing from the field.</p>\n<p>When used, the character may make an @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Intimidation]{Intimidation} @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Test]{test} against all targets in an area (as opposed to a single victim as usual). Place the edge of a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Large Blast Template} adjacent to the character. Every creature, friend and foe, within the circle must roll against the hero's @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Intimidation]{Intimidation} total.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Bugbear, Half-orc, or Orc, Intimidation d8+"},"grants":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173285,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"RDbeJwbOQcMjUg2K","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mark of Storm","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast one of the following spells:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Barrier]{barrier}</em><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\"> (air and water trapping only, not including Damage or Deadly)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\"><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Light/Darkness]{darkness}</em> (air and water trapping only)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\"><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Elemental Manipulation]{elemental manipulation}</em> (air and water trappings only)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The heir has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. She automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Raises]{raise} for 2 additional Power Points. She may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>The @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Lyrandar]{Mark of Storm} doesn't grant access to Edges requiring an Arcane Background. If the heir also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges, abilities, or Power Points can be used with the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Lyrandar]{Mark of Storm} (and vice-versa).</p>\n<p>Additionally, pick any one of the following skills: @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Boating]{Boating}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Piloting]{Piloting}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}, and add +1 to the total whenever they are used.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Half-elf"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172650,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"RFP3pPCEDDKC4pjp","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Khyber's Wrath","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-fist-strike.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Infernaalists channel fiery, Infernal power that can boil flesh and melt bone. Once this Edge is taken, the diabolist&rsquo;s <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.QBm57hlOSWLmnk0I]{bolt}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.xJxrn9AfGtpqfhll]{blast}</em>, and <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.mK0tJHKFKIeyarLg]{burst}</em> powers cause +2 damage.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Infernalist)"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171853,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"RSFjK89cXeIm3o5x","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Primal Magic","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vines-face-glow-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Primal Magic adds +2 to the damage of any power that causes damage such as <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.xJxrn9AfGtpqfhll]{blast}</em>, <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.QBm57hlOSWLmnk0I]{bolt}</em>, <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.mK0tJHKFKIeyarLg]{burst}</em>, or <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.FC8ifOJDwA3wPPGN]{damage field}</em>.</p>\n<p>If the caster rolls a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.hCxcCUCRxHOWcNGS]{Critical Failure}, however, primordial energies flood into the world, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.D2Z390QR9ROJwxMy]{Stunning} everyone in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Large Blast Template} centered on the caster (including the caster!).</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Shaman)"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171883,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"RZnD6urTiLlDGI4J","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Master and Commander","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Crews who serve under these skilled leaders add +2 to their @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Piloting]{Piloting} rolls.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Smarts d8, Command, Boating d10+, Intimidation d8+, must be sole Captain of the vessel when the Edge is used"},"grants":[],"source":"50 Fathoms"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172780,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"SF7a2a5gU1iAaNTI","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Favored Powers","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-silhouette.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ce260dx4lpo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"},"journal-links":{}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The caster has dedicated his time to mastering a particular spell, miracle, or infusion.</p>\n<p>Choose two of your character&rsquo;s powers. She may ignore up to two points of <em>any</em> penalties (@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.SCUBDmyy2SM0Ef9r]{Multi-Action}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ih5SJibOjuXkxey4]{Wounds}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.tGBCnKkDi55VRxgm]{Fatigue}, etc.) when activating that power.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Power Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Any), arcane skill d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172905,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"SKdsapdnUGkU9Rzs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Siege Mentality","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The character has a strong defensive mentality and understands how to make the most of his fortification and its defenders.</p>\n<p>When he leads the army, he increases the Siege Bonus of any fortification he defends by +1.</p>\n<p>If he makes a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Battle]{Battle} roll at the start of a siege, he can increase this bonus by an additional +1 for success and +2 with a raise by studying and better defending weak areas.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Smarts d8+, Command, Battle d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172796,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"SMa3TYZWiF9O001k","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"_id":"SPDP555oFBt8LfFo","name":"Work The Room","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-unity-alliance.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tbo7kidroy","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Social Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.U2pALBBG9geRa2S6"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Your hero's words don't just inspire those they're directed at&mdash;they often inspire others as well. Once per turn, you can use Work the Room to roll an additional skill die when @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Support]{Supporting} with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Persuasion]{Persuasion} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Performance]{Performance}. The additional die Supports any other ally who can see or hear your hero, and applies to their next action, whatever it may be.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Social Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173213,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Channel Energy","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-grey.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Clerics can cast the <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.I0mcegEN4B92V3gq]{healing}</em> power at a Range of Spirit rather than Touch. Their healing power also has the Additional Recipients Power Modifier, allowing them to heal nearby allies at the cost of one extra Power Point each.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Cleric)"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Pathfinder"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171755,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"SW5f765xgnXclqAz","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Close Fighting","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This Edge is for skilled knife-fighters and pugulists, who pride themselves on defeating their foes up close and personal.</p>\n<p>A Close Fighter armed with a knife or similar small weapon (DM&rsquo;s call) choose a single adjacent target as a free action each turn. Their attacks and @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.idEEdHIeNSogKRGm]{Parry} for that foe (only) increase by the target&rsquo;s @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.PTDRRY03N4bzcRak]{Reach} +1</p>\n<p class=\"example\"><strong>Example: </strong>A Lhazaar pirate with Close Fighting battles a Lyrandar heir with a cutlass ( @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Reach]{Reach} 0 ). The pirates @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Parry]{Parry} is raised by +1.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Fighting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172221,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"SbcxlSdA5Htqwk7h","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Arcane Background (Necromancer)","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/orb-hands-humanoid-yellow.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6ak50axz9H7wzyf6"},"cf":{"id":"temp_2i5x75676ju","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Arcane Background (Necromancer)]{Arcane Background (Necromancer)}</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Background Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171674,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"Sl7VKiVBetJSsFs5","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Master Alchemist","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/toxins/cauldron-pot-bubbles-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Alchemists craft permanent potions like any other (see @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.620eXVOwguVjobRa]{Crafting Magic Items}). Some are particularly adept at it, however, and can create potent potables while traveling using alternate ingredients.</p>\n<p>Master Alchemist allows the scientist to create potions at half the usual cost and as if she had access to Simple Workshop as long as she has her alchemist&rsquo;s bag or makeshift supplies the GM feels contain necessary ingredients or reasonable facsimiles.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Alchemist), Alchemy d10+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171856,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"TDYnY5DBKCwjebpb","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Arcane Background (Artificer)","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/orb-hands-humanoid-yellow.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_2i5x75676ju","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Arcane Background (Artificer)]{Arcane Background (Artificer)}</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Background Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171632,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"TQpExxzH33PBxdmt","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Take The Hit","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Fighters, barbarians, gladiators and the like must learn to endure violent lives filled with merciless brutality. A character with this Edge has learned to survive under the most relentless conditions. He gets a free reroll on @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.CJOnuNywSJDpO7hK]{Soak rolls} made to eliminate @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ih5SJibOjuXkxey4]{Wounds} or @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Vigor} rolls to resist @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.wmmbjJLJfMXwMcKf]{Knockout Blows}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Iron Jaw, Vigor d10+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172514,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"TiUaVUOohsAZqXFl","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Trap Sense","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.uZSxRkVLgxzgUxxR"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Many adventurers become adept at spotting and defeating all but the most clever snares and traps. They get a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.PQJiYUSX6MD02KkQ]{Notice} roll anytime a detectable trap is about to be sprung within 5&rdquo; (10 yards). They must have line of sight to the trap and can&rsquo;t be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.fN6mUVj1Lkxtr9HE]{Shaken} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.D2Z390QR9ROJwxMy]{Stunned}. This works generally like @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.9cza6SAtrQtss67d]{Danger Sense} but applies only to mechanical and magical traps.</p>\n<p>If the trap is detected and may be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ZQs1BaqxvPq86odR]{Evaded}, the rogue and anyone she warns ignores 2 points of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ZQs1BaqxvPq86odR]{Evasion} penalties to do so. If the trap can&rsquo;t normally be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ZQs1BaqxvPq86odR]{Evaded}, anyone warned may Evade at the usual &minus;2 penalty.</p>\n<p><strong>Disarming Traps:</strong> A character with Trap Sense ignores up 2 points of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.WT0ARsSIm2WDQbW3]{Thievery} penalties when attempting to disarm traps.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Repair d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173113,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"TmM0aluQBycnYTlR","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Killer Instinct","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.QomybVyELXkYseoC"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\"><p>This hero hates losing. He gets a free reroll in any opposed @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Test]{Test} he initiates</span> </p></div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172398,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"Tqq91TFfxwqASTKs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Inquisitive","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"},"journal-links":{}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Investigators spend a great deal of time researching ancient legends, working the streets, or deducing devilish mysteries. Some of these heroes are actual inquisitives while others are sleuthing mages in a fantasy world or inquisitive college professors stumbling upon Things Man Was Not Meant to Know.</p>\n<p>Investigators add +2 to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Lore]{Lore} rolls and @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice} rolls made to search through desks for important papers, sift through stacks of junk mail for something of note, or spy obscured items from piles of junk or debris</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d8+, Lore d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173035,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"U1BHSc8oduMJ8HXf","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"_id":"UHJk4sB6Il2X8MTI","name":"Connection","type":"edge","img":"icons/commodities/treasure/bust-carved-stone.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_kouunmqxeo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Glory Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p><strong>Times may be taken: </strong>4</p>\n<p>At some point a hero is likely to gain Glory by aiding certain organizations, whether directly or indirectly. When a hero gains a Connection, he must pick a specific group, as per the Edge of the same name. The hero does not belong to the organization&mdash;he simply has friends among their number willing to assist him (though he may, at the DM's discretion, be offered membership as well).</p>\n<p>The Connection should be appropriate to the character's background and his deeds. For instance, a hero who slays many lycanthrope beasts likely attracts the attention of the Church of the Silver Flame, whereas one who stops an outbreak of disease caused by a plague demon might find House Jorasco are favorable toward him.</p>\n<p>Note that the hero still needs @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Persuasion]{Persuasion} and @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Networking]{Networking} for this benefit to be of any use. Just because he's renowned, it doesn't mean the Connection will drop everything and come to his aid with exactly what he wants.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Glory Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"40+ Glory"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172670,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Double Shot","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Double Shot allows an archer to fire two arrows in one attack with a regular bow or hurl two thrown weapons as a single attack.</p>\n<p>As a limited action, the character rolls two @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.L2Z2vXl1K5GMZCXm]{Shooting} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.SzVzIV8ZxqKg3Oe3]{Athletics} (throwing) dice instead of one (this does not increase the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.QBFpTcZGY0ubXHLI]{Rate of Fire}, does not incur Recoil, and uses two projectiles). Each die hits and causes damage separately. (The Wild Die may replace either shot as desired.)</p>\n<p>The attacker must have a handy source of projectiles to accomplish the feat (a quiver, knives on a bandoleer, etc.)</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Athletics d8+ or Shotting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172253,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"UXm4OEFx3nUDsq6A","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Improved First Strike","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.VvOkBymSBDlItXnA"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Once per round, as long as he's not @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Shaken} or @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.37hOhcNkT98KKtAv]{Stunned}, the hero gets a free @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} attack against three foes immediately after he moves into @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Reach]{Reach}. (See </span><strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Free Attacks]{Free Attacks}</span></strong>).</span> <br /><br /></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, First Strike"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172330,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"UfTFLC84dRrsfRFL","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mystic Powers (Barbarian)","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-silhouette.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ce260dx4lpo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Qt3tD20Pgq0u9P9k"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>In worlds where magic is relatively common, disciplined adventurers may learn a few simple powers to help them in their quests. Choose one of the packages below. The character has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. As a limited free action, the hero automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a raise for an additional 2 Power Points. She may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>Mystic Powers doesn&rsquo;t grant access to Edges that require an Arcane Background, but she may take the Power Points or Soul Drain Edge. If the hero also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges or abilities can be used with Mystic Powers and viceversa.</p>\n<p>Abilities noted as &ldquo;Self Only&rdquo; do not get any additional benefit from that Limitation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Aii4dhYLbc4Xf8mf]{Boost Trait}</em> (<em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.MIvf1ckXhEyM27uv]{Fighting}</em>, <em>Strength</em>, <em>Spirit</em>, or <em>Vigor</em> only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.hUoU4cSN6b5UmO4f]{Smite}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.ldVHKdr9G926Rz0s]{Speed}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>All have the Self Limitation.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Power Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Strength d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172939,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"UkHF2T0R5bRhyc2p","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Rapid Shot","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.5sylgaYUqEpY9GDI"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The shooter is practiced at taking quick and accurate shots. When she's armed with a weapon that can be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Reload]{Reloaded} as a free action, and has enough arrows to do so, she may increase her weapon's @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Rate of Fire]{Rate of Fire} by 1 for any one of her @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Shooting]{Shooting} attacks that turn.</span></p>\n<p>Rapid Shot may be used with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Rapid Reload]{Rapid Reload}.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Shooting d6+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172453,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"V2U913VvyMRfXk2e","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Master Artificer","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-silhouette.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ce260dx4lpo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Z5thwi3zWWr2HXC1"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The master artificer gains and additional 250 gp progress for each success and a raise on his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Arcana] roll when crafting magical items with no limit to the total progress made per roll.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Power Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Arcane Background (Artificer) or Craft Arcane Device, Arcana or Repair d10+"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172922,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"VH2W8YXmXHkVvfmN","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Brutal","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The character with this @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.MAcvE2WNI1eEy4R8]{Edge} is more dangerous when roughed up. When determining melee damage, he adds his wound level to the roll. A hero with 3 wounds, for instance, adds +3 to his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} damage rolls.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Wild Card"},"grants":[],"source":"Lankhmar"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172206,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"VMfod6Kl4kiket4j","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Monster Hunter","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The character is completely immune to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Fear]{Fear} checks from one broad type of creature, such as ghosts, werewolves, vampires, or constructs. If applied to spellcasters, it includes the fear spell as well.</p>\n<p>The Dungeon Master is the final arbiter of whether or not the Edge applies to a particular horror.</p>\n<p>The Edge may be taken multiple times, each applying to a different creature type.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Spirit d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Horror Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173058,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"VPRuVpKvQjRgoSi9","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mark of Finding","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the following powers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Boost/Lower Trait]{boost Trait}</em>&nbsp;(<em>@UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Agility}, @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}</em>, and <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.WT0ARsSIm2WDQbW3]{Thievery}</em>)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Darksight]{darksight}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Locate]{locate}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Boost/Lower Trait]{Boost Trait} </em>and <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Darksight]{darksight} </em>have the range of touch only, but the heir gains no benefit from the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Limitations]{Limitation}.</p>\n<p>The heir has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. She automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Raises]{raise} for 2 additional Power Points. She may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>The @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Tharashk]{Mark of Finding} doesn't grant access to Edges requiring an Arcane Background. If the heir also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges, abilities, or Power Points can be used with the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Tharashk]{Mark of Finding} (and vice-versa).</p>\n<p>Additionally, pick any one of the following skills: @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Thievery]{Thievery}, and add +1 to the total whenever they are used.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Half-orc, Human, or Orc"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172614,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"VSDFLgWavWAcaZXF","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mystic Powers (Paladin)","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-silhouette.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ce260dx4lpo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Qt3tD20Pgq0u9P9k"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>In worlds where magic is relatively common, disciplined adventurers may learn a few simple powers to help them in their quests. Choose one of the packages below. The character has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. As a limited free action, the hero automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a raise for an additional 2 Power Points. She may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>Mystic Powers doesn&rsquo;t grant access to Edges that require an Arcane Background, but she may take the Power Points or Soul Drain Edge. If the hero also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges or abilities can be used with Mystic Powers and viceversa.</p>\n<p>Abilities noted as &ldquo;Self Only&rdquo; do not get any additional benefit from that Limitation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Aii4dhYLbc4Xf8mf]{Boost Trait}</em> (<em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.MIvf1ckXhEyM27uv]{Fighting}</em>, or <em>Spirit</em>&nbsp;only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.I0mcegEN4B92V3gq]{Healing}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.KdYR8YGpA9b66t6U]{Protection}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.cNNVPH3ZikrS8Qy5]{Sanctuary}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.hUoU4cSN6b5UmO4f]{Smite}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>All but <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.I0mcegEN4B92V3gq]{Healing}</em> have the Self Limitation.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":