{"name":"Natural Swimmer","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/group.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_yg4ulkebj5","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Your hero wasn't literally born in the water, but some might believe he was. He takes to it like a fish and can hold his breath longer than most others. Natural swimmers add +2 to their @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} roll for swimming, add +1 to their @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#movement]{Pace} swimming, and can hold their breath 50% longer than others of their species.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Background Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"},"grants":[],"source":"50 Fathoms"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172147,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"eRjK5dwhJh1ZqTzo","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Beast Bond","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.2DgugORlrVDyNh1z"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Some individuals have an extra&shy;ordinary bond with their animal companions. These characters may spend their own @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.NUjlHH5PBpH1dlzH#bennies]{Bennies} for any animals under their control, including mounts, pets, familiars, and so on.</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173305,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"eX8dayYQjegZmc9B","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Symbiont Mastery","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The adventurer has stronger control over attached symbionts and benefits from increased vitality from the attached symbionts. She gains a +2 bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Spirit} rolls during any battle of wills between her and the symbiont (see Intelligent Relics in Fantasy Companion). While at least one symbiont is attached, the adventurer also gains a free reroll on @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#soak-rolls]{Soak} rolls.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173349,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"ec9RATFxEp7rnjCq","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
