{"name":"Greater Mark of Sentinel","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the additional following power:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Warrior's Gift]{warrior's gift}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Warrior's Gift]{Warrior's gift}</em> has the range of touch only, but the heir gains no benefit from the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Limitations]{Limitation}.</p>\n<p>He may now also access any Epic Power modifiers to any powers offered by his dragonmark.</p>\n<p>Additionally the dragonmarked heir gains 5 more Power Points for his dragonmarked powers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mark of Sentinel"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172590,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"mfoRCp2gitzKaZ4F","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
