{"_id":"n3hQTimoSpRWo5pm","name":"Deceptive","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-unity-alliance.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tbo7kidroy","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Social Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.zdPgYpK71mwhnRCa"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Lies, deception, and misdirection are a stock-in-trade for this rogue. When making a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.z8VbTEJUItMTSxNw]{Test} based on @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts}- or @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Spirit}-linked skills, he can choose whether the target resists with @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts} or @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Spirit}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Social Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Smarts d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173157,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Scavenger","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.vrxN4g2VOcvV9nmP"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Once per encounter the hero may find, &ldquo;suddenly remember,&rdquo; or dig up some much-needed piece of equipment, a handful of ammunition, or some other useful device.</p>\n<p>The Dungeon Master decides what constitutes an encounter, and has the final word on what can and can't be found.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Luck"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173338,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"n4EmxrXxixBcL1Ai","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Aura of Courage","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.2DgugORlrVDyNh1z"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A field of holy energy encircles this noble being. Allies within 10&rdquo; (20 yards) add +2 to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1I49uf3kBthnzIjh]{Fear} checks and subtract 2 from @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-tables.eFx9Ps1fjej2opRg]{Fear Table} results.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173302,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"nIQ4gMIt75QotAqs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Fanaticism","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This Edge is most appropriate for members of the military, but the leader of a seasoned band of monster hunters might develop it as well.</p>\n<p>Troops under command of a character with this Edge add +2 to their @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Fear]{Fear} checks and subtract 2 from rolls on the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-tables.Fear Table]{Fear Table}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fervor"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172753,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"nNegBJgI7YgDOO7R","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Improved Rapid Shot","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.5sylgaYUqEpY9GDI"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The shooter is practiced at taking quick and accurate shots. When she's armed with a weapon that can be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Reload]{Reloaded} as a free action, and has enough arrows to do so, she may increase her weapon's @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Rate of Fire]{Rate of Fire} by 1 for any two of her @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Shooting]{Shooting} attacks that turn.</span></p>\n<p>Improved Rapid Shot may be used with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Rapid Reload]{Rapid Reload}.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Rapid Shot"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172367,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"niBW8dZYDMd8XEeS","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Born in the Saddle","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Whether it's on the back of fast horse or other more exotic mount, this hero feels more at home in the saddle than on her own two feet.</p>\n<p>The Edge grants the hero one free reroll on all @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Riding]{Riding} rolls and increases her mount's Pace by 2 and its running die one step.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Riding d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173017,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"njEt2LN0gWPWLQHa","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Improved Scamper","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nsyr9ljpuke","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Species Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The halfling can move so quickly as to cause multiple opponents to interfere with each other's attacks. Opponents get no @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Ganging Up]{Ganging Up} bonus against the halfling.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Fantasy Companion</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Scamper"},"grants":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173249,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"nvJrhjOx9bqcaxJs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Hard To Kill","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.hpC41I3Bd56WPTu2"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This adventurer has more lives than a herd of cats. He may ignore his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Wound} penalties when making @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Vigor} rolls to avoid <strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Bleeding Out}</strong></span>.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172297,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"nvmoR154C6EJElHP","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Improved Frenzy","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.qCULTUzDesDoGxZ6"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The fighter rolls an extra @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} die with up to two Fighting attacks in the same turn</p>\n<p class=\"example\"><strong>Example:</strong> Red desperately attacks a giant crab-like creature on an alien planet. She has Improved Frenzy and decides to attack three times (a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Multi-Actions]{Multi-Action} at the usual penalty). She rolls her Fighting skill with an extra die for her first attack and second attack. She doesn't get the extra die on her third Fighting roll.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Frenzy"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172334,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"o7KgOngTO75Hy6q7","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
