{"name":"Formation Fighter","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The warrior has trained to fight alongside others, overwhelming their common foe with synchronized strikes and blows. She adds +2 to the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Ganging Up]{Gang Up} bonus instead of +1. The maximum @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Ganging Up]{Gang Up} bonus is still +4 no matter how many Formation Fighters stand together.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Fighting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172272,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"sytnSFGn4s8Ci60D","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Calculating","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.glTPSIKamM7Kz5ex"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A few seconds to study your foe's actions gives your hero a major advantage. When his @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#action-cards-(initiative)]{Action Card} is a Five or less, he ignores up to 2 points of penalties on one action that turn, which can include @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Multi-Actions]{Multi-Action}, cover, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Range]{Range}, and even @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Wound} penalties</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172215,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"tKht60ezOFsCRsSw","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Greater Mark of Storm","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the additional following power:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Havoc]{havoc}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>She may now also access any Epic Power modifiers to any powers offered by his dragonmark.</p>\n<p>Additionally the dragonmarked heir gains 5 more Power Points for her dragonmarked powers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mark of Storm"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172601,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"tjWk8NzUb6XZdWWs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Fast Mount","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Mounting or dismounting a horse counts as an @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Actions]{action}. An adventurer with this edge can mount and dismount as a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Actions]{free action}, but may only perform one of each maneuver per round. Thus, the character could mount and dismount in one round, but he couldn't mount, dismount, and remount in the same round.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Riding d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173033,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"topGcy9RuT60yjvK","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Death before Dishonor","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The character has led his army to many victories, and the men have come to accept retreat as a stain on their honor.</p>\n<p>The character gains +2 to @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Spirit} rolls when rolling for Morale in a Mass Battle.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Spirit d8+, Hold the Line, Battle d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172748,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"tx0dpCTb0wsMPe2M","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"_id":"u6LGz3mjr3JTExuo","name":"Bolster","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-unity-alliance.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tbo7kidroy","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Social Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.zdPgYpK71mwhnRCa"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Belittling or humiliating an enemy can also boost your ally's spirits. When this character successfully @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Test]{Tests}</span> </span>a foe, he may also remove the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.vsS5QN7dPw9CFsBo]{Distracted or Vulnerable}</strong></span><strong> </span></strong>state from one of his allies.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Social Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173148,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Really Dirty Fighter","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Your character is extremely skilled in tactical deceit. Should he get a raise on a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.z8VbTEJUItMTSxNw]{Test}, he gains @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.wmmbjJLJfMXwMcKf]{The Drop} against that opponent until the foe is no longer @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.V7Z5r3YBhotQNciO]{Distracted or Vulnerable}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Dirty Fighter"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172456,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"unBPX9s6T5Yjv9RB","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Artificer's Armor","type":"edge","img":"icons/commodities/tech/tube-chamber-lightning.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pd62r7GIA9niR8AO"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The tinkerer modified his armor with cleverly placed springs, elastic straps, and reinforced bracers.</p>\n<p>As long as the tinkerer wears at least leather armor and has four hours and some material odds and ends to make the proper adjustments, he can reduce the Minimum Strength of leather armor (+2) or greater by one die type. He may apply any one of the following effects with a minute&rsquo;s work and a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.ulIbGY2fO4OPZsTI]{Repair} roll (and may choose a different effect later if he likes):</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-heading\">ARMS:</span> The tinkerer adds +2 to his melee damage and gets a free reroll on Strength rolls (not damage rolls).</li>\n<li><span class=\"list-heading\">TORSO:</span> Increase the Armor value of the chest and back by +2.</li>\n<li><span class=\"list-heading\">LEGS:</span> The tinkerer can jump twice his normal distance and adds +4 to his Pace.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Breakdown:</strong> Any time the wearer suffers a Wound, roll a die. Odd, the armor&rsquo;s additional effect falls apart and requires four hours work and a Repair roll to replace the appropriate mechanisms.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Artificer)"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171748,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"uxd8yZdGdDi6QnmJ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Greater Mark of Passage","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the additional following power:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Fly]{fly}</em></li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Teleport]{teleport}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>All powers have the range of touch only, but the heir gains no benefit from the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Limitations]{Limitation}.</p>\n<p>He may now also access any Epic Power modifiers to any powers offered by his dragonmark.</p>\n<p>Additionally the dragonmarked heir gains 5 more Power Points for his dragonmarked powers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mark of Passage"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172584,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"uzaUPh2ocGFlhObY","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Combat Reflexes","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.F66qOIh8BheHxTt1"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Your warrior recovers quickly from shock and trauma. He adds +2 to his rolls when attempting to recover from being @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Shaken} or @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.37hOhcNkT98KKtAv]{Stunned}</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172230,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"v2ilesqzJbOAd5CA","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Combat Acrobat","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.BOJbu8OiNaFrS4rG"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The tumbler leaps quickly about so that attacks against her are made at -1 as long as she's aware of the attack, can reasonably move about, and isn't suffering any @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Gear Notes]{Encumbrance} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Minimum Strength]{Minimum Strength} penalties.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Acrobat"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173019,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"vI9I5Jv5CJ1wbepB","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"_id":"vQ4VfoiAsUJxsMAD","name":"Leader of Men","type":"edge","img":"icons/commodities/treasure/bust-carved-stone.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_kouunmqxeo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Glory Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p><strong>Times may be taken: </strong>4</p>\n<p>Not every hero wants to be a leader of men, but those who do quickly find others respond well to them in times of stress, like a battle.</p>\n<p>The character may take a Leadership Edge immediately. He must meet all the requirements of the Edge as normal. </p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Glory Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"40+ Glory"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172699,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Block","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Through hard-fought experience your hero has learned to defend himself in vicious hand-to-hand combat. His @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.idEEdHIeNSogKRGm]{Parry} increases by +1 and any @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Ganging Up]{Gang Up} bonus against him is reduced by one.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172197,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"vW6iwuD3mWJmsC7L","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Stunning Blow","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The character&rsquo;s blows are powerful or precise enough to stun his foes. If he strikes an opponent with a blunt weapon (a hammer, maul, mace, his hands, etc.) and causes at least a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.fN6mUVj1Lkxtr9HE]{Shaken} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.ih5SJibOjuXkxey4]{Wound} result, resolve damage and any attempt to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.CJOnuNywSJDpO7hK]{Soak}. Then the victim must make a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Vigor} roll or be @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.D2Z390QR9ROJwxMy]{Stunned}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Strength d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172490,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"vavSGotwKSkG6UvB","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Mark of Hospitality","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_gpnez7cqj7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast the following powers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Conjure Item]{conjure item}</em> (Create Food and Water only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Elemental Manipulation]{elemental manipulation}&nbsp;</em>(no Weather)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Empathy]{empathy}</em> (humanoids only)</li>\n<li><em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Slumber]{slumber}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The heir has 10 dedicated Power Points that recharge normally. He automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Raises]{raise} for 2 additional Power Points. He may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired (at the usual cost).</p>\n<p>The @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Ghallanda]{Mark of Hospitality} doesn't grant access to Edges requiring an Arcane Background. If the heir also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges, abilities, or Power Points can be used with the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-lore.House Ghallanda]{Mark of Hospitality} (and vice-versa).</p>\n<p>Additionally, pick any one of the following skills: @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Common Knowledge]{Common Knowledge}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice}, @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Persuasion]{Persuasion}, or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival}, and add +1 to the total whenever they are used.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Dragonmarked Edges","isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Halfling"},"grants":[],"source":"Savage Eberron"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172623,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"vjkPuzUY0yJAWS5i","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"_id":"w0hyYQtygXSHgPCh","name":"Iron Will","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-unity-alliance.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tbo7kidroy","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Social Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HU2HXRsEL2JC5Egh"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The hero now adds his @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Strong Willed]{Strong Willed} bonus to resist powers and negate their effects. Iron Will doesn't stack with @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Brave]{Brave}, nor does it apply to subse&shy;quent rolls resulting from powers such as being @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Shaken} by a damaging @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Powers]{power}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-powers.Fear]{fear}, or the like.</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Social Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Brave, Strong Willed"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173165,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Linguist","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/group.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_yg4ulkebj5","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Background Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.z2ytMGrpWTKSUvJA"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This world-traveler has an ear for languages. Characters know a number of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Languages]{languages} equal to half their @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts} die type automatically.</p>\n<p>Those taking this Edge know a number of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Languages]{languages} equal to her @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts} die type instead.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Background Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6+"},"grants":[],"source":"SWADE"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172137,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"w2Vm0dliVegbxYNY","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Master Storyteller","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Tales of brave heroes and epic battles are told across Khorvaire in taverns and around hearths and campfires. Most master storytellers are skalds or bards.</p>\n<p>When using the Variable @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Glory and Infamy]{Glory} Awards rules (p. 100), the characters roll d8s instead of a d6s if this hero recounts their deeds.</p>\n<p>In addition, the storyteller is adept at deflecting bad press through carefully chosen words. The party suffers no penalties to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Glory and Infamy]{Glory} if the storyteller rolls a critical failure, treating it as a regular failure.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Smarts d8+, Persuasion d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"Hellfrost"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173054,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"xBzCcrYPHm8oGYah","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Wind Sense","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The character has an almost supernatural knowledge of air and wind. He can sense changes in the weather and wind direction long before they actually happen.</p>\n<p>If the character is piloting a ship he gains +1 to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Piloting]{Piloting} rolls during @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Nautical Contact]{Nautical Contact}, using his knowledge of the winds to outrun and catch prey.</p>\n<p>In addition, the character may draw two cards during a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Storms at Sea]{storm} and keeps the best as long as the Captain heeds his warnings. If the character has the @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Storm Chaser]{Storm Chaser} Edge as well he draws three cards.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d8+, Boating or Piloting d8+"},"grants":[],"source":"50 Fathoms"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173354,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"xMBP75bRQVmUQDax","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Defender","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[{"_id":"zlQg0Cnkg8cDuOsp","changes":[{"key":"system.stats.parry.value","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","label":"Block","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.HBNdlqoSuo47ToyJ"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>You can share your shield&rsquo;s @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.idEEdHIeNSogKRGm]{Parry} and cover bonus with one adjacent ally as a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.3hnO73iW7lBLAsHB]{Free Action}. Shield bonuses don&rsquo;t stack, so use only the highest if a character is protected by more than one.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d6+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172239,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"xiZEiDuqeavCu7r0","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Extraction","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_wbd74crjrma","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.1CK70JoA0jwY1HZI"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>When a character withdraws from melee, adjacent attackers get a free @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} attack against him (see </span><strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Withdrawing From Melee]{Withdrawing From Melee}</strong>). This is a very dangerous proposition for most, but not your wily champion.</span></p>\n<p>When moving away from adjacent foes, one of them (player's choice), doesn't get his free @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} attack.</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Combat Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172256,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"xpHrMjbrrf9PLmX0","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Fervor","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.1YojkCJvf0HcVCzU"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A simple phrase uttered by a great leader can sometimes have momentous results. A commander with this ability can inspire his troops to bloody fervor by yelling a motto, slogan, or other inspirational words. </span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Wild Cards and Extras]{Extras} in range add +1 to their @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} damage rolls</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Spirit d8+, Command"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172762,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"xxJTXuVcIMnKEYs7","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Help Me!","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_u9f0tp9vn2","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Once per round when a foe moves adjacent to the hero, the threatened character may call for help. One ally within the character's command radius who has not yet acted this turn may try to interrupt as if he were on @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Hold]{Hold}. With a success, the ally must attack the opponent who triggered this Edge.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Leadership Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Command"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703172765,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"y6S6MKAg3AVgsAnZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Healer","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.hLEyGLRY5rb99759"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>A hero with this Edge adds +2 to all @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.3 Healing]{Healing} rolls, whether natural or magical in nature.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173330,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"yDnIUXLsTbD5qRF9","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Liquid Courage","type":"edge","img":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","effects":[{"_id":"5f5punVk9GcL8wd6","changes":[{"key":"system.attributes.vigor.die.sides","mode":2,"value":"2","priority":null},{"key":"system.wounds.ignored","mode":2,"value":"1","priority":null},{"key":"system.attributes.smarts.die.modifier","mode":2,"value":"-1","priority":null},{"key":"system.attributes.agility.die.modifier","mode":2,"value":"-1","priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp","label":"Liquid Courage","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null,"origin":null}],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ueibkknhw27","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.MkvhQtL8RUJrsGj9"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This gregarious individual processes alcohol far differently than most. The round after consuming a stiff drink (about eight ounces of hard liquor or equivalent), her @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Vigor} increases one die type (increasing @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1 Making Characters]{Toughness} as well). The drinker can also ignore one level of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Damage Effects]{Wound} penalties (which stacks with other abilities that do the same).</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Smarts}, @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.F3QL0OVOOYJiYIoO.JournalEntryPage.VWEUOsd2rvNu6ch9]{Agility}, and all linked skills suffer a &minus;1 penalty for the duration, however.</p>\n<p>The effect lasts for one hour after it begins, at which point the boozer suffers a level of @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigue} for the next four hours.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Weird Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Vigor d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173335,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"ydTN4GYg2EfcGXGp","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Bladedancer","type":"edge","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nsyr9ljpuke","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Species Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Bladedancers are elite elven warriors, this Edge is their trademark combat maneuver. Despite the name, they may use weapons.</p>\n<p>When used, an elf spins and dances about, attacking every opponent in his path like a deadly cyclone. On the tabletop, the character makes a running roll and must move that many inches. He may not double back.</p>\n<p>Every target adjacent to the fighter's path, starting with his initial position, is attacked at &minus;2. One small downside to this Edge is that every adjacent target must be attacked&mdash;whether friend or foe. Individual targets may only be attacked once while using this Edge.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Elf, Agility d8+, Fighting d8+, Two-Weapon Fighting"},"grants":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173238,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"ykq4vTSpbEUkeKxZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Dirge","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-singing-voice-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1EMcGBXdZi6N5iYA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_lfv57yk1te","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Arcane Edges","color":"#000000"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>This baleful performance builds dread among the bard&rsquo;s foes. At the bard&rsquo;s discretion, any enemy within 10&rdquo; (20 yards) and line of sight who spends a @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.RkejkA1MLhB8IeFe]{Benny} to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.CJOnuNywSJDpO7hK]{Soak} or reroll a Trait or damage roll subtracts 2 from the total.</p>\n<p>The bard must be able to speak, sing, or play her instrument to use this ability.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Arcane Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Arcane Background (Bard)"},"grants":[],"source":"Fantasy Companion"},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703171785,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"ysOODPDgFTxPcF7E","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
{"name":"Woodsman","type":"edge","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-merchant-scribe.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_j9emv9z81ds","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-edges.mTY5axyUKXjsEmmx"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>Woodsmen are rangers, scouts, and hunters who are more at home in the wilderness than in urban areas. They are skilled trackers and scouts, and know how to live off the land for months at a time.</span></p>\n<p>Woodsmen add +2 to @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Survival]{Survival} rolls, and @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Stealth]{Stealth} rolls made in the wild (not towns, ruins, or underground).</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"category":"Professional Edges","isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d6+, Survival d8+"},"grants":[],"source":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.2.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1675703173123,"lastModifiedBy":"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf"},"_id":"zR3AsTgH8E0GepJA","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7YwiyXiAhNBZZlLf":3}}
